{"word":"G357 - ἀναλογίζομαι - analogízomai - an-al-og-id'-zom-ahee - Consider","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναλογίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">analogízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-al-og-id'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consider</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நினை"},{"paragraph":"to think over, ponder, consider"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G356 - ἀναλογία - analogía - an-al-og-ee'-ah/356\">G356</a>; to <i>estimate</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>contemplate:</i> - consider.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}